Argued June 1, PAYNE, Respondent, v. PAYNE, Appellant. (No. 73761) 497 P2d 374 Dale Pierson, Salem, argued the cause for appellant. With him on the brief were Cfoodenough, Evans & Pierson, Salem. Norman K. Winslow, Salem, argued the cause for respondent. With him on the brief was Howard Kaffun, Salem.

affirmed June 1, 1972

Before Schwab, Chief Judge, and Langtry and Thornton, Judges.
